List series

Source: R/db.R
db_series.Rd

List series

Usage

db_series(
  series_ids,
  facets = FALSE,
  observations = FALSE,
  metadata = TRUE,
  format = "json",
  align_periods = FALSE
)

Examples

# \donttest{
db_series("AMECO/ZUTN/EA19.1.0.0.0.ZUTN")
